						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Abhirāma Varatuṅga Śaka 1517, Regnal year 10 = 1595 A.D. Vīra Pāṇḍya.</hi></p>						

						<p>The details of date given in the record viz., Maṉmata, Aṟpaśi 25 do not admit for verification. It refers to the institution of <hi rend="italic">abhishēkha-Kaṭṭaḷai</hi> to the deity Tirukkaḷāvuḍaiya-tambirāṉār and mentions a certain Pāṇḍyadēva (name lost).</p>						

